BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:NfbLuBOoJtPIsTuCuyy_P
SUMMARY:Collections—A Live Magazine and Public Club
DTSTAMP:20260402T030253Z
DTSTART:20260401T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:Collections—A Live Magazine and Public Club hosted by Ariel Bas
	om is a monthly showcase of both live readers and video performances featu
	ring a diversity of positions\\\, styles\\\, and modes: poetry juxtaposing
	 story\; literary fiction opposing memoir\; drama next to genre fiction. \
	\nDo you want to be a part of this community? Do you want to be a reader? 
	Show up to the event\; introduce yourself\; we are welcoming to all writer
	s and hold space for new members of our public club. \\nWe create an envir
	onment we can be proud of by treating ourselves and each other with high r
	egard by leading with kindness and by wearing our favorite fancy clothes. 
	We are not casually stumbling in but rather we show up as our best selves 
	in order to present our best work. \\nVisit arielbasom.com/collections for
	 monthly line-ups\\\, more details\\\, and archives of past collections. \
	\nFree admission to this event is made possible with support from 4Culture
	.\n\nhttps://hugohouse.org/event/_2026-04-01/\n\nFrom Hugo House
URL:https://hugohouse.org/event/_2026-04-01/
X-CALRIPPER-SOURCE:hugo-house
CATEGORIES:Hugo House
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT3H
END:VEVENT
