UID:mywzsRWW72gTsBiW-LAud
SUMMARY:Hot Meal Program (dinner)
DTSTAMP:20260402T030253Z
DTSTART:20260406T150000Z
DESCRIPTION:In addition to providing a meal\\\, the Hot Meal Program provid
	es a safe environment to feel cared for and to feel like a part of this ne
	ighborhood. We offer a variety of hygiene products\\\, gently-used clothin
